name: APPEA
notes: The Australian Petroleum Production & Exploration Association is the peak national body representing Australia's oil and gas exploration and production industry. APPEA's vision is to achieve a growing and internationally competitive Australian oil and gas industry that makes a vital and sustained contribution to the nation's economy.

name: Drilling Contractor
notes: Get oil and gas drilling news, videos, ebooks, and more. Drilling Contractor is the official magazine of the International Association of Drilling Contractors. The website is dedicated to all things drilling and completions and offers enhanced editorial to complement the print magazine, including animations, videos, additional graphics, and content to help readers keep up with the newest trends in the industry.

name: Offshore Engineer
notes: Here you can read Offshore oil and gas news, news on LNG, shale, exploration, operations and production. Since 1975, Offshore Engineer (OE) has been the go-to source for engineering and technology news and features. OE offers multiple ways to stay up-to-date on the latest technology and trends necessary to help you do your job.

name: Oilfield Technology
notes: Oilfield Technology is the premier source of technical & analytical information for the global upstream oil and gas sector. Find the latest upstream news, events, and interviews from the oilfield industry, including oil rigs, drilling, oil fracking, and offshore & onshore projects.

name: Oilman Magazine
notes: Oilman, a prominent oil and gas business magazine, offers comprehensive coverage of industry news, technology, exploration, and production. With a keen focus on shale markets and software, it serves as a leading resource for professionals seeking insights into the dynamic oil and gas sector.

name: Oilnewskenya
notes: Latest Oil and Gas News from East Africa, Also hydrocarbon exploration, geothermal, drilling, discoveries, pipeline, wind and solar energy  news. Also have a view of some of Production Sharing Agreements between governments in the region and various oil companies exploring for oil and gas.

name: World Oil
notes: World Oil, established in 1916 as The Oil Weekly, is published monthly by Gulf Energy Information. World Oil provides news, oil prices, data, statistics, shale reports and upstream industry trends relating to the exploration, drilling, completion and production of oil and gas, both onshore and offshore.

name: Yahoo! Finance: Oil & Gas Drilling & Exploration Industry News
notes: The latest news on the Oil & Gas Drilling & Exploration industry from Yahoo! Finance
